{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had no longer can-- it's no longer self-supporting, that is, no mutual support.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because here my reserve company has taken on another mission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was very angry about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't have any choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- I wanted to get on and say, well, send the reserve battalion in there, see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what they should have done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was a battalion in reserve following me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, anyway, since I was the closest to it, they-- somebody was antsy to get it right away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, I then got-- I immediately got ahold of the reserve company commander, which was Company I of the 157th and explained the mission to him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the camp was a little-- oh, maybe a mile off to the left of where I Company was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, I don't know why or what we're, we're going to run into there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I'll go with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'll give you an extra platoon of machine guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took a machine of-- a platoon of machine guns from I Company-- or from M Company, which is a heavy weapons company, and attached it to I Company, so they'd have extra firepower.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not take any tanks because the tanks were already committed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't think I'd need tanks anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So somewhere around afternoon, around 1 o'clock, we approached the camp [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then could, could see the walls.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't see anything inside because it just looked like an ordinary German military post to us from the outside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a masonry fence maybe 8 feet high or something like that around where we entered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw the entrance to the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But from the outside, it was just like a regular, German military post.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
